title: Husky Liners “The Forces” - X-act Contour Product Features
description: Meet the Force family. They stay active and like to push their SUV to the limit. The Husky Liners® X-act Contour® perfectly matches the contours of your truck or SUV and brings together indestructible strength with a soft, comfortable cushion. Add to that a premium look and our exclusive features and you’ve got liner gold. Punch it, slap it, flick it, kick it. Can you feel it?
